svt_i2c_slave_transaction_base_sequence Class Reference

Inheritance diagram for class svt_i2c_slave_transaction_base_sequence:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This sequence raises/drops objections in the pre/post_body so that root sequences raise objections but subsequences do not.
